{"tid":1702314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【首爾遊行集會悼念周梓樂】","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T05:08:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c823ac4f15ebb8c99c372026c869b011308a23a4","tid":1702314,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"韓國首爾今日（9 日）有市民和當地港人發起遊行和燭光集會，悼念昨日去世的科大學生周梓樂，並表態聲援香港。參與人士以燭光砌出周梓樂的中文名字，並以粵語和韓語高唱《願榮光歸香港》，民陣副召集人黎恩灝亦有到場發言。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awc4DXH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fawc4DXH.jpg&h=e037bbd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHMhev2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHMhev2.jpg&h=733791bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xdh4DXJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdh4DXJ.jpg&h=dfcd6942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/laiyanhoeric/photos/pcb.2157770847861475/2157770751194818/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flaiyanhoeric%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.2157770847861475%2F2157770751194818%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=4b734579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/laiyanhoeric/photos/pcb.2157770847861475/2157770751194818/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n（相片來源：民陣副召集人黎恩灝 Eric Lai）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/2600334916718779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F2600334916718779&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpv1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=1836c52b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/2600334916718779</a>"},{"pid":"dfe6f515d9524a3f9504ce690218f745ffec9c0e","tid":1702314,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:26:52